{"lastModified":1748862974655,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::bd22f3a0-3ac8-11f0-88ea-a1ae8e35448e","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nWhile staying faithful to Lagoon’s DNA, this new generation of catamarans are recognized by a personal style that has emerged. An individually streamlined and accomplished design complimented by her large portholes and panoramic views gives you a catamaran meant for you.\n\nThe Lagoon 40 is no exception to our unsurpassable catamaran design expertise. Celebrated for its expressive approach to the sailing experience, this catamaran is your family’s ideal getaway.\n\nWith a unique dimension of tranquility, this catamaran is designed for you and your relaxation at sea. A comfortable cockpit looking out to sea, a starboard dining table—able to accommodate up to twelve guests, a recreational area on the same side, and seating at the rear beam gives you ample space for entertaining and enjoying your life at sea.\n\nAn ergonomic helm station is accessible from the cockpit and deck enabling a constant communication between the skipper and crew. It’s hard to miss any excitement with this layout design.\n\nA spacious swimming platform between the large aft transoms allows simple access to the tender and a safe, easy boarding process from land or water.\n\nThe cockpit is fitted with a sunbathing area which offers you even more living space to enjoy and soak in your life at sea.","blueprint":{"name":"TARTARUGA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd22f3a0-3ac8-11f0-88ea-a1ae8e35448e::assets::9cdd77d0-3aca-11f0-bca5-310fe65e9447/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd22f3a0-3ac8-11f0-88ea-a1ae8e35448e::assets::9ce95eb0-3aca-11f0-bca5-310fe65e9447/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd22f3a0-3ac8-11f0-88ea-a1ae8e35448e::assets::9cbde1e0-3aca-11f0-bca5-310fe65e9447/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd22f3a0-3ac8-11f0-88ea-a1ae8e35448e::assets::9ce12150-3aca-11f0-